Date: Wed, 15 Nov 2000 13:56:02 +0100
From: Juan Cuadros <jcuadros@efd.net>
Source: Diario El Pais, 15 Nov 2000 [edited

Seventeen patients [have been hospitalized, 4 of them in serious
condition, due to
an outbreak of [legionellosis. The health authorities are investigating
the source of the infection localized in the neighborhood of "La
Barceloneta". The outbreak was detected on Monday. Four patients are in a
[life-threatening condition. Local authorities, in collaboration with the
Generalitat of Catalunya started yesterday the studies to detect the source
of the infection.
--
Dr. Juan Cuadros Gonzalez
